    <title>day1</title>
    <link href="/2023/12/26/day1/"/>
    <url>/2023/12/26/day1/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>暂且把今天当作 day1 吧。</p><p>回家的时候赶上勋望放学，沿溯阻绝。干等半个小时。</p><p>到家四点半了。</p><p>到现在才过去 3 小时，哥们却险些死于电子阳痿。</p><p>群里冷冷清清的：群友要么忙于工作，要么忙于学业。</p><p>我百无聊赖地刷b站，想要找到些许慰藉。</p><p>就在这时我找到了慰藉。</p><p>音乐。</p><p>正如我所说的，哥们的歌单都是靡靡之音：</p>        <div id="aplayer-qRMFUWrZ" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>  <script>  var options = {"narrow":false,"autoplay":false,"showlrc":3,"mode":"random","music":[{"title":"ぱられループ を歌ってみた (**平行的轮回**parallel loop) (Jeku remix)","author":"Jeku/aori","url":"https://dlink.host/musics/aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmVkcnYtbXkuc2hhcmVwb2ludC5jb20vOnU6L2cvcGVyc29uYWwvc3Rvcl9vbmVkcnZfb25taWNyb3NvZnRfY29tL0VYbk8tRGpoQ1BkSnZOTFRSaVpiZUpzQkdaY3JzQ2F2eGtjV2JnZFR0eHpOcEE.mp3","pic":"https://p1.music.126.net/d0wC3QrLl6hQPOMxIXFZBg==/109951169011778614.jpg","lrc":"data:application/octet-stream;base64,"},{"title":"world.execute(me);","author":"mili","url":"https://dlink.host/musics/aHR0cHM6Ly9vbmVkcnYtbXkuc2hhcmVwb2ludC5jb20vOnU6L2cvcGVyc29uYWwvc3Rvcl9vbmVkcnZfb25taWNyb3NvZnRfY29tL0VjQTdWa1NJVWJsTmlxaW1mQ3c5ZGNZQjRHSTAwVzZSU25SaThoc1BqTXJPTXc.mp3","pic":"https://p1.music.126.net/-OxCLbGs-JxKtPaBCo1yuw==/18801648835570109.jpg","lrc":"data:application/octet-stream;base64,"}]};  options.element = document.getElementById("aplayer-qRMFUWrZ");  var ap = new APlayer(options);    window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);  window.aplayers.push(ap);  </script><p>然后这一天就结束了。</p><p>晚安。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
